William.

98
00:03:37,341 --> 00:03:39,442
Drafting class is helping me
redecorate around here.

99
00:03:39,510 --> 00:03:41,144
You see, I have Nationals
over the weekend,

100
00:03:41,212 --> 00:03:42,912
and I expect to return
with a comically large

101
