You know what it
has to look like?

106
00:03:53,324 --> 00:03:56,726
Elvis' gold record
room at Graceland.

107
00:03:56,794 --> 00:03:58,728
Except I'll be wanting
far fewer morbidly obese

108
00:03:58,796 --> 00:04:00,764
