will be crushed.

118
00:04:22,119 --> 00:04:23,687
Sue, can I see your trophy?

119
00:04:23,754 --> 00:04:24,921
Sure, Will.

120
00:04:24,989 --> 00:04:25,955
Hope and dream.

121
