{hissing}

182
00:07:54,732 --> 00:07:55,965
Yeah, I did it.

183
00:07:56,033 --> 00:07:58,368
And I'm proud. All I did
was step up and be a man.

184
00:07:58,435 --> 00:08:00,169
They got what was coming
to them.

185
00:08:00,237 --> 00:08:01,371
